  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>You'll have a buffet breakfast where you can enjoy a variety of pastries, fresh fruit, bread and hot options. You’ll also find some typical Ligurian products including focaccia and honey from Mount Portofino.</p>
<p>Half Board is available for a supplement and includes a four course dinner, with choices, at Restaurant Principessa.</p>
<p><strong>Restaurant Principessa</strong> offers a Mediterranean menu using high quality ingredients. Enjoy freshly-caught fish, local olive oil and delicious wines. The wine list is varied and includes the local DOC Golfo del Tigullio.</p>
<p><strong>La Conchiglia Beach Restaurant</strong> is right on the beach and is a casual spot for a light lunch or refreshments.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
