  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Exclusive Beach Club</strong></p>
<p>Hotel guests have access to a beach club with sandy beach, children's playground, bar, restaurant and free Wi-Fi (normally open June to mid September, payable locally for approx. €50 per day for two sun loungers and an umbrella and a towel)</p>
<p><strong>Family facilities</strong></p>
<p>Hotel Regina Elena is a great choice for families. Children will enjoy the kid’s club, located in the beach club, with activities for children between 3-12 years old. There are plenty of games including painting, treasure hunts and dancing, as well as a dedicated children’s pool.</p>
<p><strong>Hotel facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Heated rooftop pool with whirlpool and panoramic views over the coastline (normally open from May to mid-October)</li>
<li>Pool and beach towels are provided</li>
<li>Bicycle hire (payable locally)</li>
<li>Fitness room</li>
<li>Table tennis</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking Garage (approx. €25 per night, payable locally, subject to availability)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
