  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Regina Elena is a family-run hotel and a great base for visiting the surrounding area. The centre of Santa Margherita is just a short walk away and Portofino can be reached by a pleasant coastal walk. This is a charming spot with lots of facilities including a fab rooftop pool with panoramic views.</p>]]></listingDescription>
