  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Garden View Rooms</strong> sleep up to three people and are located at the back of the hotel. They overlook the gardens and hills towards Mount Portofino. Rooms that sleep up to three people are available on request. </p>
<p><strong>Partial Sea View Rooms </strong>sleep up to two people and have views of the Gulf of Tigullio and the gardens around the hotel.</p>
<p><strong>Front Sea View Rooms </strong>sleep up to three people and have a balcony. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms </strong>with a french bed are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Slippers</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of approx. €4 per person per night is payable locally (max 10 nights, guests aged 15+).</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
